data.description: Take advantage of this move-in ready, Oakleaf Plantation stunner! You'll love the updates including a brand-new roof, all new flooring, new cabinets and countertops, fresh interior paint and more. The first floor offers a spacious family room, formal dining room, and 5th bedroom with accompanying bathroom perfect for guests or an office. The kitchen is equipped with an open floor plan, plenty of cabinets, and a food prep island. Upstairs features 4 bedrooms including the owner's suite with a walk-in closet, a laundry room, and a bonus loft great for entertaining or can be converted to a sixth bedroom. Enjoy the summer months at the amazing community water park. You'll also love the large yard backed to the nature preserve. Schedule an appointment to come see this beauty!
